data.description: PREPARE TO BE IMPRESSED. NEW HOME BUILT IN 2020 WITH OVER 1,500SF. 3 BEDROOM, 2 1/2 BATH 2-STORY CUSTOM BUILD ON PRIVATE RESIDENTIAL STREET WITH A DETACHED 2-CAR GARAGE. EVERYTHING FROM ROOF/SIDING/FLOORING FROM THE GROUND UP BUILT IN 2020. STYLISH OPEN-FLOORPLAN ON THE MAIN LEVEL WITH THE LIVING ROOM/DINING AREA & KITCHEN IS PERFECT FOR TODAY'S HOMEOWNERS. SPACIOUS 1ST FLOOR PRIMARY 16X10 BEDROOM WHICH INCLUDES A WALK-IN CLOSET & FULL, PRIVATE BATHROOM. 32" WHITE CABINETS ACCENTUATE THE GRANITE COUNTERTOPS & FLOORING. BARN DOOR PANTRY IN THE KITCHEN! POWDER ROOM ALSO INCLUDES THE WASHER & DRYER.
